    text-align: center;padding:10px 0 0 50px; max-height:76px; background:#fff;"><a alt="Now Open: Preview the New Zoho Mail" href="/mail/new.html" target="_blank" title="Now Open: Preview the New Zoho Mail"><img alt="Now Open: Preview the New Zoho Mail" src="https://www.zoho.com/mail/images/new-ui-exclusive.png" title="Now Open: Preview the New Zoho Mail"></a></div></div><div class="features-head"><div class="content-wrap"><h2>Email Designed with Business Users in Mind.</h2></div></div></div></div><div id="benefits" class="clearfix content-wrap"><ul><li class=""><div><span class="feature-icon1"></span><h4><a href="/mail/advanced-features.html">The Best of Both Worlds.</a></h4><p>Experience a clean, fast Webmail with features matching or superior to those found in desktop email clients. Take control of your Inbox, and free yourself from software upgrades. </p><a href="/mail/advanced-features.html">/mail/advanced-features.html</a></div></li><li class=""><div><span class="feature-icon2"></span><h4><a href="/mail/webmail.html">No Ads, Privacy Guaranteed.</a></h4><p>At Zoho, we value user data and privacy. We never display ads, even in our free plans, and your email exchanges are never scanned for keywords. </p><a href="/mail/webmail.html">/mail/webmail.html</a></div></li><li class=""><div><span class="feature-icon3"></span><h4><a href="/mail/online-office-apps.html">Email plus Online Office.</a></h4><p>The Zoho Mail suite includes Zoho Docs. Your team can create, edit and collaborate on text, presentation and spreadsheet documents using the most sophisticated online editors. Work faster and improve productivity with an online office. </p><a href="/mail/online-office-apps.html">/mail/online-office-apps.html</a></div></li><li class=""><div><span class="feature-icon4"></span><h4><a href="/mail/control-panel.html">Smooth Setup &amp; Management.</a></h4><p>Quickly set up email with a step-by-step setup wizard. Easily manage email policies, groups, mailbox quotas, and more using an extensive Control Panel. </p><a href="/mail/control-panel.html">/mail/control-panel.html</a></div></li><li class=""><div><span class="feature-icon5"></span><h4><a href="https://www.zoho.com/security.html">Secure &amp; Reliable.</a></h4><p>As a provider of more than 25+ apps that go beyond email, Zoho products are protected with multiple layers of secure infrastructure, and have a 99.9 percent uptime guarantee. </p><a href="https://www.zoho.com/security.html">https://www.zoho.com/security.html</a></div></li></ul></div><div id="product-image-html-block"><div class="content-wrap"><div class="field-home-page-raw-html"><div class="more-features"><a href="features.html">Explore More Features</a></div></div></div></div><div id="ph_testimonial"><div class="content-wrap"><div class="z-slider-wrap enable-nav enable-auto-slide"><ul class="z-slider"><li class=""><span class="author-image"><img typeof="foaf:Image" class="img-responsive" src="//iz.zohostatic.com/sites/default/files/mail-testi.png" width="91" height="84"></span><span class="author-name">@Maribel C. Ibrahim </span><p></p><p>"Finally gained control of my Inbox with @zoho - amazing webmail client which is the best, hands down! Thx! "</p></li></ul></div></div></div><section class="bot-banner-wrap"><div class="content-wrap"><h2>Host Your Business Email</h2><div class="get-started"><a href="zohomail-pricing.html">Get Started Now</a></div></div></section></div></section></div></section></div></div></div><!-- maincontainer end --><div class="footer-wrapper"><footer><div class="region region-footer"><section id="block-zoho-navigation-links-product-pages-footer-links" class="block block-zoho-navigation-links clearfix"><div class="footer-sec-wrap"><div class="content-wrap"><div class="footer-links-wrap"><div class="product-links one-column"><div><ul><li><a href="/mail/features.html" title="">Features</a></li><li><a href="/mail/mobile/" title="">Mobile Apps</a></li><li><a href="/mail/zohomail-pricing.html" title="">Pr